      "date": "2013-03-08 16:53:14.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nThis change to osd_statfs() doesn't make sense. Essentially you are changing os_bavail to always be (OSD_GRANT_FOR_LOCAL_OIDS / osfs->os_bsize) unless the filesystem is so full that the original os_bavail is smaller...\n\nThe intent of that function is to reserve some space for local file updates.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
